{"tid":100650,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"孫中山曾發佈行政命令廢除農曆新年","createTime":"2017-01-30T08:10:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-02T21:09:18.000Z","uid":22675,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2e6c03245ab8e9b092167dd5ec564931f6c1494d","tid":100650,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T08:10:46.000Z","msg":"<strong>呂秋遠：春節休假　要感謝國民政府改革失敗</strong><br />\n<br />\n2017年01月27日11:28<br />\n<br />\n1917年，也就是民國6年，在國民政府教育部工作的魯迅先生，1月1日到1月3日，他的日記中都只有記載「休假」兩個字，直到1月4日才去上班。<br />\n然而，時至1月23日至26日，也就是農曆的除夕到初三，他卻都到教育部上班。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，不只是這一年，從1912年民國開始，所有的政府機關，就是元旦開始放三天，但是農曆春節沒有任何假期，因為 國父孫中山先生，在當選大總統後，就像川普一樣發佈行政命令，也就是《臨時大總統改曆改元通電》，要求廢除陰曆，改用陽曆，春節假期完全取消。<br />\n<br />\n後來袁世凱繼任大總統，又通過內政部發佈命令，<span style=\"color: red;\">要求中國人從1913年起，與傳統農曆完全分手</span>，舉凡端午節、重陽節、元宵節、春節、七夕等等傳統節日，一律改成按照陽曆計算。"},{"pid":"0a388b4231ea0cabe7e9b9f2b40c915e9c222420","tid":100650,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T08:11:48.000Z","msg":"袁世凱可不是開玩笑的，1913年，除了政府機關一律依法休假，農曆新年必須上班，不得請假外，陽曆新年也必須全面放假，不得上班。袁世凱為此事還安排專員督導各單位，以徹底廢除農曆。<br />\n而如果有民眾在農曆春節期間的北京城放鞭炮慶祝，一律逮捕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n這個創舉，應該比起現在的一例一休還要狂。<br />\n<br />\n不過，中國實在太大了，又是軍閥割據時代，北洋政府的命令其實不能號令全國，例如四川就照樣過農曆新年，炮竹聲仍然不絕於耳。直到1918年，北洋政府只好放棄這項「改革」，讓民眾照樣過農曆春節。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>不過，廢除農曆這個念頭，在國民政府的心中，一直沒有消失。</strong>特別是因為北洋政府默許農曆，廣州的 蔣公政府當然要廢除農曆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n特別是到了1928年，廣州國民政府統一中國，定都南京，在5月7日那一天公佈法令，要求「<span style=\"color: red;\">嚴禁私售舊曆、新舊曆對照表</span>」，意思是以後讓民眾不知道農曆初一是哪一天。<br />\n<br />\n「嚴令京內外各機關、各學校、各團體，除國曆規定者外，對於舊曆節令，一律不准循俗放假」，所以取消所有春節假期，除夕當然不能放假。另外通令「各省區市妥定章則，公告民眾，將一切舊曆年節之娛樂、賽會等一律加以指導改良，按照國曆日期舉行。」<br />\n<br />\n<strong>到了1930年，全國正式實施廢除農曆</strong>，屈原變成是陽曆（或者叫做國曆）5月5日跳江自殺、中秋節固定在陽曆的8月15日，所以那一天不一定會月圓、初一變成元旦，以突顯國民政府革命進取、與世界接軌的決心"},{"pid":"f4f5031ee319e64ddb3149309e6a279cd64e9d21","tid":100650,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T08:19:00.000Z","msg":"唔奇，孫中山跟日本，日本又廢左農曆新年<br />\n<br />\n但日本人到今日都好似仲係叫星期金木水火土日月"},{"pid":"f95f946a763f0934f6d88d1989739ab24551eb55","tid":100650,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T08:31:12.000Z","msg":"係香港應該行唔通<br />\n<br />\n因為變相無左四日假期, D港豬同你死過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e9bff9a0781f145f1f885b59765cbe836d01a05","tid":100650,"uid":57705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T08:42:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5126d533c2b95068dade706629073f795f169190","tid":100650,"uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T08:51:01.000Z","msg":"國民政府係專指十四年廣州成立至憲法總統前個個政府, 乜鬼野民國六年國民政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e17cb5e11744fc5777165c79cfb36ab4a5fd93b7","tid":100650,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T11:24:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a17a6485c3f49f5d0252f8fc9b70c6cbc09ce06","tid":100650,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T12:12:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8caa143f18be94b35eda2997e8baaebe1029b12f","tid":100650,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T12:22:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>國民政府係專指十四年廣州成立至憲法總統前個個政府, 乜鬼野民國六年國民政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n國民黨北伐<br />\n推翻武昌起義成立原中華民國<br />\n另建立一黨專政俄共式中華民國國民政府"},{"pid":"aeb095eccf3077e5a59e721ac86c0048d883b81c","tid":100650,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T14:00:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fa85e9412fb79a88d046afd993166234e1de513","tid":100650,"uid":36014,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T14:05:29.000Z","msg":"其實孫大炮仇視自身華人文化既行為真係好撚on 9 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71ac4fb4f4e805e21dda8fc9f49dd8ee9069ec1a","tid":100650,"uid":54627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T14:55:32.000Z","msg":"民國六年 (1918年) 應該得北洋政府同一堆軍閥咋喎"},{"pid":"5b598a08248d0c422c3b0a805f87798ae72214b2","tid":100650,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T15:16:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>民國六年 (1918年) 應該得北洋政府同一堆軍閥咋喎</blockquote><br />\n國民政府教科書係咁講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02c876f1b28cc8f26b9b91518765720b53ff991c","tid":100650,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T14:12:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50e89f33c440850d30dc5f515d6b2f867f4cbfd6","tid":100650,"uid":17510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T15:12:49.000Z","msg":"篇文有頭無尾既<br />\n<br />\n咁最後係點<br />\n點解而家都無廢到<br />\n<br />\n共匪既取態又係點？<br />\n當今台灣係咪仲有新舊並行？"},{"pid":"756d7c60e95ec7d4c5c5600fcc0a923b527ecc16","tid":100650,"uid":13503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T15:13:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77f4e41e441e0a16d2214db8c0512058a22cfaad","tid":100650,"uid":17510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T15:50:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屍變<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae4cb605820746881c11a4fb34e94a41ccda9d85","tid":100650,"uid":63233,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T15:53:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9725863de021aaef662143b790c617808d502b55","tid":100650,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T15:55:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>篇文有頭無尾既<br />\n<br />\n咁最後係點<br />\n點解而家都無廢到<br />\n<br />\n共匪既取態又係點？<br />\n當今台灣係咪仲有新舊並行？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但是這樣的措施引起了中國各地的反彈，勉強實施四年以後，國民政府只能在1934年又通令全國，取消強制廢除陰曆，「對於舊曆年關，除公務機關，民間習俗不宜過於干涉」。 <br />\n<br />\n從此以後，中國人才又可以光明正大的過春節。 <br />\n<br />\n所以，我們明天可以放假，其實得來不易，國民政府曾經差點把春節殺掉，我們要珍惜明天開始的好時光，努力打牌、認真花錢、享受美食、到處遊玩，不要再浪費這先賢先烈幫我們爭取到的美好時刻了。 <br />\n<br />\n至於減肥的事，明年再說吧！ <br />\n<br />\nlink:<a href=\"http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20170127/1044869/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Fnew%2F20170127%2F1044869%2F&d=6VpbUQS5Cy4QwgKrD6%2Fp7m6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=2f89292c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20170127/1044869/</a>"},{"pid":"e6af95d54424c8825d65c043b8dd962067953342","tid":100650,"uid":16461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T15:58:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>篇文有頭無尾既<br />\n<br />\n咁最後係點<br />\n點解而家都無廢到<br />\n<br />\n共匪既取態又係點？<br />\n當今台灣係咪仲有新舊並行？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但是這樣的措施引起了中國各地的反彈，勉強實施四年以後，國民政府只能在1934年又通令全國，取消強制廢除陰曆，「對於舊曆年關，除公務機關，民間習俗不宜過於干涉」。 <br />\n<br />\n從此以後，中國人才又可以光明正大的過春節。 <br />\n<br />\n所以，我們明天可以放假，其實得來不易，國民政府曾經差點把春節殺掉，我們要珍惜明天開始的好時光，努力打牌、認真花錢、享受美食、到處遊玩，不要再浪費這先賢先烈幫我們爭取到的美好時刻了。 <br />\n<br />\n至於減肥的事，明年再說吧！ <br />\n<br />\nlink:<a href=\"http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20170127/1044869/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Fnew%2F20170127%2F1044869%2F&d=6VpbUQS5Cy4QwgKrD6%2Fp7m6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=2f89292c\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20170127/1044869/</a></blockquote><br />\nOn9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe54fd20441009280095ba44560dea35803de1c6","tid":100650,"uid":17510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T16:01:06.000Z","msg":"其實好想知而家係由咩人制定農曆同新曆曆法？<br />\n古有司天監  而家係天文台？？"},{"pid":"98a4bd31be8ec8f113136f7b257b5293cbfafbb6","tid":100650,"uid":1082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T17:47:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔奇，孫中山跟日本，日本又廢左農曆新年<br />\n<br />\n但日本人到今日都<span style=\"color: red;\">好似仲係叫星期金木水火土日月</span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係跟五行，係跟拉丁文或者西方星象<br />\n<br />\nSunday -- Sun's day, 拉丁文係dies solis 日躍日<br />\nMonday -- Moon's day, 月躍日<br />\nTuesday -- dies Martis, 姐係day of Mar<br />\nWednesday -- dies Mercurii, 水躍日<br />\nThursday -- dies Iovis, 木躍日<br />\nFriday -- Freya's day， dies Veneris, 金躍日<br />\nSaturday -- Saturn's day, dies Saturni, 木躍日<br />\n<br />\n至於東亞既七曜，其實都係係唐朝由印度傳入，其實都係歐洲野黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"559fd1a0c17258997fb981284ab1443d1b925a13","tid":100650,"uid":653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T21:09:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係香港應該行唔通<br />\n<br />\n因為變相無左四日假期, D港豬同你死過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n港豬只會含淚返工"}]}